            "recommended_reading": `<div id="tab-select"> <p class="ftab-active" id="start">Development</p> <p class="ftab">Reading</p> <p class="ftab">Next Mod</p> <p class="ftab">Credits</p></div><div style="text-align: left;margin: auto 5em;"> <span id="rpage0" style="display: inline-block;"> <h2>Tough as Texas</h2> <h3>by TheMcCain</h3><p>Thanks for playing Tough as Texas! This was my 2nd mod, and it was really fun to make, even though it took a really long time.<br><br>In real life, Ted Cruz lost the primary mainly because of Donald Trump. Ted Cruz was an ardent conservative, but even then Donald Trump's rhetoric just appealed to primary voters more. In all honesty, Donald Trump would probably run third-party if Ted Cruz won the nomination, just out of spite, but I wanted to give the player a realistic chance and I also didn't want this to be a 2016 New Day clone.<br><br>There is actually already a 2016 Ted Cruz mod, but it's very old, made by Enviromental_Cap104. Although it's age is very apparent, it does offer a look back into a simpler time of TCT modding, and it helped me figure out how I wanted to structure this.<br><br>Also, believe it or not, this was supposed to be a 2016 Jeb Bush mod. The writing was getting boring though, and if I didn't change course, this was gonna start looking like a 2016N, so I decided to go for a more bombastic character, where I landed on picking Ted Cruz.<br><br>I'd like to give a special thanks to theanswerisme for his great work on this mod, to littleamericanman_85501 for making the banner, and to all of our amazing playtesters on Reddit and Discord. This mod wouldn't have reached it's full potential without them!</p></span> <span id="rpage1" style="display: inline-block;"><h2>Reading</h2><p><h4>The Primaries</h4><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ted_Cruz_2016_presidential_campaign" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ted Cruz 2016 Presidential Campaign</a><br><a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/donald-trump-gop-convention-2016-how-he-got-here/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Trump Primary Victory</a><br><a href="https://youtu.be/Un3OhYs-tCE?si=jSnYoZSFnWaUH4PX" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Full CBS News South Carolina Republican Debate</a><h4>2016 Presidential Election</h4><a href="https://www.brookings.edu/articles/why-hillary-clinton-lost" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hillary Clinton: Good President, Bad Candidate</a><br><a href="https://www.politico.com/story/2016/11/election-results-2016-clinton-trump-231070" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Donald Trump: Greatest Upset in History?</a><br><h4>Further Helpful Links</h4><a href="http://youtube.com/watch?v=PCHJVE9trSM" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hillary Clinton's “Deplorable” blunder</a><br><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vgHNFXJgRw0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ted Cruz/Carly Fiorina Interview - April 29th, 2016</a><br><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2016_Republican_Party_presidential_primaries" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">2016 - General Republican Primary Info</a><h4>Books by the Candidates</h4>\rTed Cruz - <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Time-Truth-Reigniting-Promise-America/dp/0062365614/ref=sr_1_3?crid=1VZF488OH1HLQ&dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.PXdNJgVLtC2EWYOQ1cgk-T9iVdYll0txji4UQaT2zaRUQ4PTl5dThJXV2uVSmoXHYZQD7wpi9OHHmszMrlVzvCRGoaoEMinglMhaY40w1zD05Zwr9toN0ET6HfgNNcn7k1DOJ6LhTWejKAvyl_uXZzMuVKDBtu7ih5Bcs2vL54-VEFPkj_hMPQO_BnyRZg6yaJwWygiPBV5xfKFmdrwuvSRv0W8MXTJZlKDOEesRzGw.bjUlwdmUjTNv1NStBu9Z0evWkkBa02E2SGJl9M1aRu8&dib_tag=se&keywords=A+Time+for+Truth&qid=1760817437&sprefix=a+time+for+truth%2Caps%2C75&sr=8-3\" target=\"_blank\">A Time For Truth</a></br>        \rTed Cruz - <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Justice-Corrupted-Weaponized-Legal-System/dp/1684513618/ref=pd_bxgy_d_sccl_1/132-5840850-8325653?pd_rd_w=kDpCL&content-id=amzn1.sym.dcf559c6-d374-405e-a13e-133e852d81e1&pf_rd_p=dcf559c6-d374-405e-a13e-133e852d81e1&pf_